description:
Jay Glazer, National Football League insider for FOX NFL Sunday, joins C&B to talk about his non-profit organization to help vets and his new book on overcoming depression. Truckers winning: 54% of Canadians want to lift covid rules. Bill Maher says we have to drop covid restrictions. DeSantis vs. Boston Mayor Michelle Wu. We were right and they were wrong. YouTube bans Virginia mom's school board speech.
